OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny mist and low cloud burning
OL,6,Foff this morning. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fday will be dry across all parts with
OL,8,Fsome lengthy spells of sunshine. Warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,11,Fsome late sunshine. Then staying dry
OL,12,Fand clear overnight with some patchy
OL,13,Fmist and low cloud. Chilly in
OL,14,Fsheltered glens.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FA dry and warm day with some
OL,17,Fsunshine although some high cloud
OL,18,Faround. Cooler onshore breeze along
OL,19,Fthe east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
